o3smeasures.astvisitors

Class LooseClassCohesionVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
      • o3smeasures.astvisitors.LooseClassCohesionVisitor

  • public class LooseClassCohesionVisitor
extends org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTVisitor
    A visitor for abstract syntax trees, that visits the given node to perform the calculation of the LCC (Loose Class Cohesion) measure.
